28:05.460 --> 28:08.263
I don't hear that very often.

28:08.363 --> 28:10.831
Must be the uniform.

28:12.033 --> 28:15.202
I could use a coffee.

28:17.436 --> 28:20.270
Shh, she's with the movie star.
- Interesting.

28:20.370 --> 28:22.006
Yeah.
- Look at gunny.

28:22.106 --> 28:24.271
A little early morning.

28:38.514 --> 28:40.215
Clear.
- Clear.

28:40.315 --> 28:42.525
Tatum, Evanson, set it up.

28:42.588 --> 28:45.051
Two short bursts, 85 rounds.

28:49.889 --> 28:51.891
Ready.
Gun set.

28:51.991 --> 28:53.991
Fire.

28:57.929 --> 28:59.996
That's good.

29:00.096 --> 29:02.298
Nice.

29:02.398 --> 29:05.133
Listen up.

29:06.402 --> 29:08.402
This is a bale.

29:08.453 --> 29:12.073
It'll make it easier to carry
the gun with a hot barrel.

29:12.173 --> 29:14.809
You won't burn your hands.

29:14.909 --> 29:17.112
Now it's not made for its
stability and accuracy

29:17.212 --> 29:20.015
But if you're in a pinch,

29:20.115 --> 29:23.217
You can shoot and move with this.

29:23.317 --> 29:25.385
Let me show you.

29:36.427 --> 29:40.592
I couldn't hit the side
of a barn with that thing.

29:44.100 --> 29:47.135
You'd better start practicing.

29:47.235 --> 29:49.235
Yeah.

29:53.174 --> 29:54.975
It's gorgeous.

29:55.075 --> 29:57.144
Come on, let's go in the water. - No.

29:57.244 --> 29:59.846
Come on, come on.
- No, I'm not going in that water.

29:59.946 --> 30:01.281
Come on.
- No way.

30:01.381 --> 30:04.050
No.
- I'll get you.

30:04.150 --> 30:06.686
I'm not gonna have you drown.

30:06.786 --> 30:10.390
No, put me down.

30:10.490 --> 30:11.925
Put me down.
