John, you're crazy.

30:25.970 --> 30:28.708
Ah.

30:31.344 --> 30:33.412
I got it.

30:44.722 --> 30:47.457
Oh no.
Oh no, you don't.

30:47.557 --> 30:50.226
Don't you dare.

31:24.618 --> 31:26.618
Attention on deck.

31:30.622 --> 31:33.023
Stand easy.

31:36.527 --> 31:40.030
Gentlemen, the 5th division
will ship out very soon

31:40.130 --> 31:43.615
For action in the Pacific theater of war.

31:43.708 --> 31:46.669
We won't know our destination
until we're well underway.

31:46.769 --> 31:49.571
But wherever we go,

31:49.671 --> 31:52.106
We will see the job through.

31:53.608 --> 31:55.809
Am I clear?
- Yes, sir.

32:00.680 --> 32:02.749
I have some more good news.

32:02.849 --> 32:05.117
Gunnery sergeant John Basilone

32:05.217 --> 32:07.852
Has decided that home can wait.

32:09.087 --> 32:12.255
He will be joining us.

32:14.024 --> 32:15.525
Carry on, gunny.

32:15.625 --> 32:17.625
Atten-hut.

32:21.633 --> 32:23.633
At ease.

32:26.642 --> 32:29.477
So is anybody scared?
- No, sir.

32:29.577 --> 32:33.681
I said is anybody scared?
- No, sergeant.

32:35.217 --> 32:37.486
You lying sacks of shit.

32:39.356 --> 32:41.357
It's good to be scared.

32:41.457 --> 32:44.160
It means you're awake,

32:44.260 --> 32:46.428
You're ready.

32:51.400 --> 32:53.534
Company dismissed.

32:57.505 --> 32:59.539
You ready?
You scared?

33:15.021 --> 33:17.589
