38:40.147 --> 38:41.781
You know...

38:41.881 --> 38:43.683
I woke up one day

38:43.783 --> 38:45.783
And I was 30 years old.

38:45.868 --> 38:48.088
Satisfied.

38:48.188 --> 38:50.908
