I need a corpsman.

41:43.300 --> 41:45.300
Move it back.

41:51.212 --> 41:54.181
Get off the beach.
Keep moving.

41:56.050 --> 41:57.652
Keep moving.

41:57.752 --> 41:59.354
Don't stop.

41:59.454 --> 42:00.922
Keep moving.

42:01.022 --> 42:03.572
Get off the beach.
Keep moving.

42:06.894 --> 42:08.628
Off the beach.
Get up.

42:08.728 --> 42:10.797
Move.

42:11.734 --> 42:14.102
Someone help me.

42:14.202 --> 42:15.937
Help him back.

42:16.037 --> 42:19.182
Off the beach.
Off the beach, get off.

42:22.241 --> 42:24.809
